      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 56,
      "message": "We will be integrating all sensitive data into AAF. As such we should store passwords as secrets and reference them here. \n\nExample from aai-champ:\n\n            - name: KEY_STORE_PASSWORD\n              valueFrom:\n                secretKeyRef:\n                  name: {{ template \"common.fullname\" . }}-pass\n                  key: KEY_STORE_PASSWORD\n            - name: KEY_MANAGER_PASSWORD\n              valueFrom:\n                secretKeyRef:\n                  name: {{ template \"common.fullname\" . }}-pass\n                  key: KEY_MANAGER_PASSWORD",
